**Sandbox (execute_python) — MANDATORY after all subagents return.**
Run ALL numeric computations below. Do NOT perform arithmetic in reasoning text.

#### A. ROIC and Peer Premium
```python
# ROIC = NOPAT / Invested Capital
tax_rate = net_income / ebit if ebit and ebit > 0 else 0.21  # default 21%
nopat = ebit_last * (1 - tax_rate)
invested_capital = total_equity + total_debt - cash
roic_pct = (nopat / invested_capital) * 100 if invested_capital else None

# Peer ROIC premium (moat signal)
peer_roic_premium_pp = roic_pct - peer_median_roic_pct if roic_pct and peer_median_roic_pct else None
```

#### B. FCF Conversion
```python
fcf_conversion_pct = (fcf / net_income) * 100 if net_income and net_income > 0 else None
```

#### C. Leverage and Coverage
```python
net_debt = total_debt - cash
ebitda = ebit + depreciation_amortization  # use D&A from cash flow statement
net_debt_to_ebitda = net_debt / ebitda if ebitda and ebitda > 0 else None
interest_coverage = ebit / interest_expense if interest_expense and interest_expense > 0 else None
```

#### D. Revenue CAGR and Margin Trends
```python
revenue_cagr_3y_pct = ((revenue_latest / revenue_3y_ago) ** (1/3) - 1) * 100 if revenue_3y_ago else None
gross_margin_pct = (gross_profit / revenue_latest) * 100 if revenue_latest else None
operating_margin_pct = (ebit_last / revenue_latest) * 100 if revenue_latest else None
net_margin_pct = (net_income_last / revenue_latest) * 100 if revenue_latest else None

# Margin trend: compare latest vs 3 years ago
operating_margin_3y_ago_pct = (ebit_3y_ago / revenue_3y_ago) * 100 if revenue_3y_ago else None
margin_trend_pp = operating_margin_pct - operating_margin_3y_ago_pct if operating_margin_pct and operating_margin_3y_ago_pct else None
# ≥+2pp = improving; within ±2pp = stable; ≤-2pp = deteriorating
```

